and made a mess.

66
00:05:00,091 --> 00:05:01,676
That night, this jerk

67
00:05:01,801 --> 00:05:04,387
sent his driver home and came here.

68
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:07,140
He singled Dong-kyu out and demanded that

69
