to arrest him for obstruction of justice.

74
00:05:19,777 --> 00:05:22,071
If we did that,
would he have gotten punished?

75
00:05:22,155 --> 00:05:22,989
He has connections.

76
00:05:23,072 --> 00:05:24,949
That's why we should let
his connections help him

77
00:05:25,033 --> 00:05:26,993
while we help our colleague.

78
00:05:28,786 --> 00:05:30,455
An Jang-mi, what's your opinion?

79
00:05:31,122 --> 00:05:32,874
I vote for covering it up.

80
00:05:34,042 --> 00:05:35,918
I don't want him to get inspected

81
00:05:36,461 --> 00:05:38,087
because of that asshole.

82
00:05:38,838 --> 00:05:40,965
His dream is to work at a station
in his hometown

83
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:43,217
while living a quiet life
with his mother and kid.

84
00:05:44,677 --> 00:05:46,637
If I fail to grant him such a small wish,

85
00:05:46,721 --> 00:05:48,389
I can't call myself his senior.

86
00:05:49,766 --> 00:05:51,350
-It's settled then.
-But

87
00:05:51,434 --> 00:05:55,229
