Hey, stop telling me about
your family matters!

112
00:07:14,684 --> 00:07:15,726
Just go home.

113
00:07:16,018 --> 00:07:17,603
I hate it when you do that.

114
00:07:47,592 --> 00:07:48,634
Aren't you going on patrol?

115
00:07:51,637 --> 00:07:53,639
Myeong-ho, we have to go on patrol now.

116
00:07:53,723 --> 00:07:55,099
-We'll leave in a bit.
-Okay.

117
