of the Criminal Investigation Division.

189
00:12:13,315 --> 00:12:15,025
Just know that you're screwed now.

190
00:12:18,154 --> 00:12:19,864
Just come and help us
if you don't want that.

191
00:12:19,947 --> 00:12:24,160
Arrive by ten o'clock.
I'll message you the location.

192
00:12:28,998 --> 00:12:30,749
Ho-cheol, where are you?

193
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:33,544
What do you think?
I'm keeping an eye on that bastard.

194
00:12:33,961 --> 00:12:35,004
Are they going to come?

195
00:12:35,087 --> 00:12:36,797
<i>-No, they aren't.</i>
-What?

196
00:12:37,673 --> 00:12:40,217
Gosh,
it'll be hard if it's just the two of us.

197
00:12:40,926 --> 00:12:42,553
It's not like we can shoot him.

198
00:12:42,887 --> 00:12:45,014
-<i>We'll shoot him if we have to.</i>
-What the...

199
00:12:45,097 --> 00:12:47,057
<i>Why should we be scared of
shooting a criminal?</i>

200
00:12:47,141 --> 00:12:49,059
Does this country allow the police
to use guns?

201
00:12:49,143 --> 00:12:51,479
All the officers that have
used firearms ended up...

202
00:12:51,562 --> 00:12:52,730
CHIEF KIM HAN-SEOK

203
00:12:53,397 --> 00:12:54,440
Chief Kim is calling.

204
00:12:54,899 --> 00:12:56,442
Ju-yeong must've told him.

205
00:12:56,525 --> 00:12:58,777
Are you scared of
getting yelled at by Chief Kim?

206
00:12:58,861 --> 00:12:59,987
<i>Hey.</i>

207
00:13:00,321 --> 00:13:02,948
