You really are.

210
00:13:09,538 --> 00:13:11,207
Shut it. Just get here quickly.

211
00:13:30,142 --> 00:13:31,143
Hello?

212
00:13:32,520 --> 00:13:33,854
Yes.

213
00:13:37,066 --> 00:13:38,943
Okay, I'll be there shortly.

214
00:14:02,758 --> 00:14:04,593
Cook your own food.

215
00:14:07,555 --> 00:14:08,514
Seriously...

216
00:14:16,397 --> 00:14:17,565
What was the call about?

217
00:14:18,274 --> 00:14:19,733
Do you have to go somewhere?

218
00:14:20,776 --> 00:14:22,820
Your grandparents are
in critical condition.

219
00:14:27,324 --> 00:14:30,244
