but nothing has actually happened.

220
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:36,083
I have to go to work.

221
00:14:38,711 --> 00:14:40,421
Call me if anything happens.

222
00:14:48,304 --> 00:14:49,346
Cook me some <i>ramyeon</i>.

223
00:14:49,430 --> 00:14:50,556
Cook it yourself.

224
00:14:51,557 --> 00:14:53,058
I'm going through puberty.

225
00:14:54,268 --> 00:14:55,352
