230
00:15:17,249 --> 00:15:18,292
<i>What?</i>

231
00:15:19,793 --> 00:15:20,878
<i>Whose mom and dad?</i>

232
00:15:21,086 --> 00:15:21,962
Mine.

233
00:15:23,172 --> 00:15:26,175
I see, your parents.
What are you going to do?

234
00:15:26,884 --> 00:15:28,594
<i>Not sure. What should I do?</i>

235
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:30,346
Well, I don't know these things.

236
00:15:30,846 --> 00:15:32,097
And I do?

237
00:15:32,181 --> 00:15:34,808
<i>Come on. You know everything.</i>

238
00:15:36,101 --> 00:15:38,646
<i>Well, I have to arrest a suspect soon.</i>

239
00:15:38,812 --> 00:15:40,606
<i>Honey, just go and see
how they're doing first.</i>

240
00:15:41,231 --> 00:15:43,943
Can you call me if something happens?
Right now, I'm...

241
00:15:45,861 --> 00:15:47,279
Asshole.

242
00:16:06,548 --> 00:16:07,675
It's that bastard's.

243
