570
00:45:39,445 --> 00:45:42,239
Who drank and jumped into the ocean?

571
00:45:42,614 --> 00:45:43,657
You're drunk.

572
00:45:46,243 --> 00:45:47,244
Let go of me!

573
00:45:48,912 --> 00:45:50,581
<i>-You...
-Who said that, you asshole?</i>

574
00:45:50,664 --> 00:45:52,749
<i>-Get off me.
-Who said that?</i>

575
00:45:52,916 --> 00:45:54,376
<i>Tell me!</i>

576
00:45:56,503 --> 00:45:57,504
Do you have a death wish?

577
00:45:57,588 --> 00:45:59,465
