We saved a man who was drowning!

584
00:46:14,021 --> 00:46:15,564
What about

585
00:46:15,647 --> 00:46:18,192
how we solved a cold case
and caught the culprit?

586
00:46:18,775 --> 00:46:19,985
Let go!

587
00:46:22,863 --> 00:46:27,284
What did you do? What the fuck did you do?

588
00:46:27,367 --> 00:46:28,660
Tell me what you did.

589
00:46:29,411 --> 00:46:30,537
Tell me!

590
00:46:31,038 --> 00:46:31,914
Come back here.

591
00:46:31,997 --> 00:46:33,332
-Yang-chon...
-Stop right there!

592
00:46:33,499 --> 00:46:34,708
-Yang-chon...
-Get back here!

593
00:46:35,501 --> 00:46:36,960
