617
00:48:07,175 --> 00:48:09,761
You're the tallest one in our class.

618
00:48:12,556 --> 00:48:14,391
You have three penalty points left.

619
00:48:16,393 --> 00:48:17,394
There's a bet going on

620
00:48:17,477 --> 00:48:19,855
