626
00:48:37,956 --> 00:48:38,790
Look down there.

627
00:48:38,874 --> 00:48:40,917
-Congratulations on graduating.
-Where are you headed?

628
00:48:49,217 --> 00:48:50,969
I heard you applied to
Hongil Patrol Division.

629
00:48:51,261 --> 00:48:54,139
That's why I gave you a popsicle.
I applied there too.

630
00:48:55,641 --> 00:48:57,434
