695
00:54:18,213 --> 00:54:20,215
You ditched the call on purpose, right?

696
00:54:20,298 --> 00:54:23,301
Will you stop it?
You're getting fired up again.

697
00:54:23,385 --> 00:54:25,095
He didn't respond on purpose, right?

698
00:54:25,178 --> 00:54:27,097
He just went on patrol in the back alley.

699
00:54:27,430 --> 00:54:29,015
-I don't know.
-I'm not sure.

700
00:54:29,140 --> 00:54:30,850
