701
00:54:30,976 --> 00:54:32,268
You don't know anything.

702
00:54:33,770 --> 00:54:37,107
Who is this, and why is he so tall?

703
00:54:37,440 --> 00:54:39,401
You. What's your name?

704
00:54:39,818 --> 00:54:41,069
I'm Yeom Sang-su.

705
00:54:41,361 --> 00:54:42,654
Who's your mentor?

706
00:54:42,737 --> 00:54:43,822
I don't know yet.

707
00:54:44,030 --> 00:54:46,950
He hasn't gotten assigned yet.
He'll be under Captain Eun for now.

708
00:54:49,202 --> 00:54:50,245
How tall are you?

709
00:54:52,330 --> 00:54:53,581
I'm about 188cm.

710
00:54:53,665 --> 00:54:55,417
Say the exact number.

711
00:54:55,500 --> 00:54:56,668
I'm 190cm.

712
00:54:58,086 --> 00:55:00,964
Don't let your height bother you,

713
00:55:01,131 --> 00:55:02,048
or you'll answer to me.

714
00:55:02,549 --> 00:55:05,427
Police officers shouldn't let
anything bother them.

715
00:55:06,594 --> 00:55:09,055
Keep that in mind.
Don't let anything bother you.

716
00:55:09,556 --> 00:55:10,473
Yes, sir.

717
00:55:12,726 --> 00:55:14,185
CHOI MYEONG-HO

718
00:55:16,229 --> 00:55:17,731
Traitor.

719
00:55:21,276 --> 00:55:22,152
Do you have a problem?

720
00:55:22,736 --> 00:55:23,820
You bet I do.

721
00:55:23,903 --> 00:55:25,613
That's enough. I'm warning you.

722
00:55:25,697 --> 00:55:27,699
You ratted out your own colleague.

723
00:55:29,159 --> 00:55:30,410
Let's fight it out.

724
00:55:30,994 --> 00:55:31,995
Pick a date.

725
00:55:34,998 --> 00:55:36,124
Damn it.

726
00:55:36,207 --> 00:55:37,208
Hey.

727
00:55:37,417 --> 00:55:39,961
Get changed. Get dressed.

728
00:55:41,504 --> 00:55:43,173
The juniors are watching.

729
00:55:43,256 --> 00:55:45,800
You're their senior.
Don't let them see you fight.

730
00:55:47,218 --> 00:55:49,095
There's nothing to see here.

731
00:55:49,763 --> 00:55:51,222
-Get dressed.
-Yes, sir.

732
00:55:54,476 --> 00:55:56,478
There are seven female officers here.

733
00:55:56,561 --> 00:55:58,980
You won't see the other four
in Group Three and Four.

734
00:55:59,064 --> 00:56:00,648
I'll be re-assigned in 2 days.

735
00:56:01,524 --> 00:56:03,359
Night shift Song Hye-ri, clean the room.

736
00:56:03,443 --> 00:56:06,071
-Han Jeong-o, you're on supplies.
-Okay.

737
00:56:06,154 --> 00:56:07,989
Locker one has cleaning supplies
for the room,

738
00:56:08,073 --> 00:56:09,491
locker two for the corridor.

739
00:56:09,574 --> 00:56:10,992
Keep everything in order

740
00:56:11,076 --> 00:56:13,244
-and that's Han Jeong-o's responsibility.
-Okay.

